function Start(idActorDamager, idActorDamaged)

	idBandit = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Bandit")[1]
	tSnakes = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Marsh_SacrificeEnemies")
	for i, Snake in ipairs(tSnakes) do
		Hydra.ActorAddAITarget(Snake, idActorDamager, true)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, szGroup)

	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(idBandit, "NPC_Idle_Sit_Ground_Wounded")
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorKill(idActorNPC)
	Hydra.ItemDropAtActor(idActorNPC, itemLeftEye)
	
end

function Start()

	idBandit = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Bandit")[1]
	Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idBandit, Hydra.TEAM_SCENERY)

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	-- Turn off region in QST_Hawe_Marsh_03
	Hydra.EventSend("LeftEyeRegionStop")
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	Hydra.SetGameVariableFlag("TempleLeftEyeReturned", true)
	Hydra.EventSend("LeftEye", idActorPlayer)
	
end
